OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1775754356
OL,3,CFacebook worker faces criminal probe
OL,4,Cfor 'downloading 30,000 private
OL,5,Cpictures'
OL,7,FA former worker at Meta is under
OL,8,Fcriminal investigation after he was
OL,9,Fsuspected of downloading around 30,000
OL,10,Fprivate Facebook images.
OL,12,FThe engineer was employed by the
OL,13,Fsocial media giant when it is believed
OL,14,Fhe designed a programme to be able to
OL,15,Faccess the personal pictures while
OL,16,Favoiding internal security checks.
OL,18,FA specialist detective from the
OL,19,FMetropolitan Police's cybercrime unit
OL,20,Fis investigating the alleged mass
OL,21,Finvasion of Facebook users' privacy.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1775754356
OL,3,CFacebook worker faces criminal probe
OL,4,Cfor 'downloading 30,000 private
OL,5,Cpictures'
OL,7,FMeta has confirmed that the suspected
OL,8,Fbreach was discovered more than a year
OL,9,Fago and the company itself referred
OL,10,Fthe matter to police in the UK.
OL,12,FIt added that affected Facebook users
OL,13,Fhave been notified, the worker was
OL,14,Fsacked and it says it has upgraded its
OL,15,Fsecurity systems.
OL,17,FThe engineer under suspicion, who
OL,18,Flives in London, is currently on
OL,19,Fpolice bail while the criminal
OL,20,Finvestigation continues.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1775754356
OL,3,CFacebook worker faces criminal probe
OL,4,Cfor 'downloading 30,000 private
OL,5,Cpictures'
OL,7,FAccording to court papers, police say
OL,8,Fhe "is alleged to have accessed and
OL,9,Fdownloaded approximately 30,000
OL,10,Fprivate images belonging to Facebook
OL,11,Fusers whilst working for Meta".
OL,13,F"It is alleged that he created a
OL,14,Fscript designed to circumvent Meta's
OL,15,Finternal detection systems, allowing
OL,16,Fhim to do so."
OL,26,@pD@DOUsD@^O]uD@AOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1775754356
OL,3,CFacebook worker faces criminal probe
OL,4,Cfor 'downloading 30,000 private
OL,5,Cpictures'
OL,7,FTwo weeks ago, two magistrates agreed
OL,8,Fto vary the man's police bail so that
OL,9,Fhe must next report to Met officers in
OL,10,FMay and inform the force of any plans
OL,11,Ffor foreign travel.
OL,13,FA Meta spokesperson confirmed the
OL,14,Fexistence of the criminal
OL,15,Finvestigation, saying: "Protecting
OL,16,Fuser data is our top priority.
OL,26,@wD@XOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1775754356
OL,3,CFacebook worker faces criminal probe
OL,4,Cfor 'downloading 30,000 private
OL,5,Cpictures'
OL,7,F"After discovering improper access by
OL,8,Fan employee over a year ago, we
OL,9,Fimmediately terminated the individual,
OL,10,Fnotified users, referred the matter to
OL,11,Flaw enforcement and enhanced our
OL,12,Fsecurity measures.
OL,14,F"We are co-operating with the ongoing
OL,15,Finvestigation."
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUwD@OO]
